Classes in model used by model

Game
          A Game object represents an instance of a Yahtzee game.
Hands
          Enumerates the possible hands in a Yahtzee game.
Player
          A Player object represents a player in a Yahtzee game.
PlayerIdentity
          Represent the immutable player identity for a Player object in a Yahtzee game.
Score
          A Score object represents a single score in a Yahtzee game, including a hand and a numeric score.
ScoreCard
          A Score Card keeps score for a certain player.
ScoreValidator
          The ScoreValidator class validates and scores hands for a Yahtzee dice game.
Status
          Enumerates the status of the Game object
Strategy
          A Strategy object should have a name, which can identify it to a user, and a takeTurn method.
